ZH: 我每天步行上班可以省下来一些钱。
EN: Walking to work every day can save me some money.

ZH: 她不买新衣服，来省下来买一个新手机。
EN: She doesn't buy new clothes to save up and buy a new cellphone.

ZH: 我们计划省下来这笔钱用来旅行。
EN: We plan to save this money up for traveling.

ZH: 她每个月都省下来一部分薪水作为储蓄。
EN: Every month she saves a portion of her salary as savings.

ZH: 如果你每天带饭，就能省下来不少钱。
EN: If you bring lunch every day, you can save a lot of money.

ZH: 我们尽量把开支控制得低一点，就能省下来一些。
EN: If we try to keep the expenses low, we can save some money.

ZH: 他们已经省下来足够的钱买一辆小车了。
EN: They have saved enough money to buy a small car.

ZH: 我们省下来的钱足够支付孩子的教育费用。
EN: The money we save up is enough to cover our children's education expenses.

ZH: 如果我省下来一些，就可以买些新家具了。
EN: If I save up some money, I can buy new furniture.

ZH: 这次旅行我打算很节俭，把省下来的钱用在其他方面。
EN: I plan to be very thrifty during this trip and use the saved money elsewhere.

ZH: 他决定省下来的钱捐给慈善机构。
EN: He decided to donate the saved money to a charity organization.

ZH: 我省下来的钱都花在了买书上。
EN: I spent the money I saved on buying books.

ZH: 如果你能省下来一些，我们可以一起去度假。
EN: If you can save up some money, we can go on vacation together.

ZH: 他努力省下来的所有钱都用来还房贷了。
EN: He used all the money he had saved up to repay the mortgage.

ZH: 我把省下来的零花钱给了父母作为生日礼物。
EN: I gave my parents the saved pocket money as a birthday gift.

ZH: 如果我每天都坐公交车，能省下来不少时间。
EN: If I take the bus every day, it can save me a lot of time.

ZH: 为了省下来一些时间，我决定开始自己做饭。
EN: To save up some time, I decided to start cooking on my own.

ZH: 我们买了便宜一点的食材，为了能省下来一些钱。
EN: We bought cheaper ingredients in order to save up some money.

ZH: 她节约开支，希望可以省下来一些钱去旅行。
EN: She is cutting down on expenses, hoping to save up some money for traveling.

ZH: 我们不去餐馆吃饭，这样能省下来不少费用。
EN: We're not eating out at restaurants, which can save us a lot of expenses.
